Symbol.Script_VL:
! ================================================================== ! Made by Csányi Bence ! 2016/09 ! ==================================================================
hideparameter all
call "ncp_text_label" parameters all
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Sizes ! -------------------------------------------------------------------------
parameters A = A, B = B, ZZYZX = ZZYZX lock "A", "B", "ZZYZX" parameters ac_bottomlevel = 0, ac_toplevel = ZZYZX
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Types ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------- values{2} "iElementType" ELEMENT_CHAIR, `Chair`, ELEMENT_SOFA, `Sofa`, ELEMENT_TABLE, `Table`
values{2} "iChairType" CHAIR_TYPE1, `1`, CHAIR_TYPE2, `2`, CHAIR_TYPE3, `3`, CHAIR_TYPE4, `4`
values{2} "iSeatPadding" SEATPAD_WO, `Without Upholstery`, SEATPAD_SEAT, `Upholstered Seat`, SEATPAD_BACK, `Upholstered Seat & Back`
values{2} "iLegType" NORMAL_LEG, `Normal leg`, OFFICE_LEG, `Office leg`
values{2} "iBackType" HIGH_BACK, `High Back`, LOW_BACK, `Low Back`
values{2} "iFeetType" FEET_STEEL, `Aluminium`, FEET_WOOD, `Wood`
values{2} "iFeetHolder" FEET_ON, `Enabled`, FEET_OFF, `Disabled`
values{2} "iArmRest" ARMREST_ON, `Enabled`, ARMREST_OFF, `Disabled`
values{2} "iPlastic" 1, `Enabled`, 2, `Disabled`
values{2} "iNumSeat" 1, `Two`, 2, `Three`
values{2} "iType" TYPE_CODA, `Coda`, TYPE_PUBLIC, `Public`, TYPE_PUBLICBARSTOL, `Public Barstool`, TYPE_RIO, `Rio`, TYPE_RIOBARSTOL, `Rio Barstool`, TYPE_RIOMINI, `Rio Z Junior og Mini`, TYPE_RIOJUNIOR, `Rio Junior`, TYPE_R48, `R-48`, TYPE_FAVN, `Favn`,
TYPE_SAMBA, `Samba`, TYPE_SAMBAJUNIOR, `Samba junior`,
TYPE_R60C, `R-60c table`, TYPE_NORDICLIGHT, `Nordic Light table`, TYPE_HUB, `HUB table`, TYPE_R80, `R-80 table`, TYPE_R100, `R-100 table`
values{2} "iSymbolDet" 1, `Scale sensitive`, 2, `Always Simple`, 3, `Always Detailed`
if iElementType = ELEMENT_CHAIR then lock "iChairType" ! főtípus beállítása kötelező minden elemnél! lock "iLegType", "iBackType" ! opciók lock "iFeetType", "iFeetHolder", "iArmrest", "iNumSeat" ! opciók lock "iPlastic" ! megmondja, hogy a szék TELJESEN műanyag vagy teljesen huzatolt lock "iPlasticType", "PlasticType" ! beállítja, hogy szék típushoz melyik plastic material készlet tartozik endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Materials ! -------------------------------------------------------------------------
call "ncp_materials" parameters all iElementType = iElementType, iType = TYPE_R48, iPlastic = iPlastic, iSeatPadding = iSeatPadding, iUpholsteryType = iUpholsteryType
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iBackType" and iBackType = LOW_BACK then parameters iFeetHolder = FEET_OFF lock "iFeetHolder" endif
if iBackType = LOW_BACK then parameters iFeetHolder = FEET_OFF lock "iFeetHolder" endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iLegType" and iLegType = OFFICE_LEG then parameters iFeetHolder = FEET_OFF lock "iFeetHolder" else iFeetHolder = FEET_ON endif
if iLegType = OFFICE_LEG then parameters iFeetHolder = FEET_OFF lock "iFeetHolder" endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Detail Level ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
values "iDetLevel3D" DET3D_NONE, DET3D_BLOCK, DET3D_DETAILED
values "detLevel3D" stDetLevel3D
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "detLevel3D" then iDetLevel3D = 1 for i = 2 to vardim1(stDetLevel3D) if detLevel3D = stDetLevel3D[i] then iDetLevel3D = i i = vardim1(stDetLevel3D) endif next i parameters iDetLevel3D = iDetLevel3D else iDetLevel3D = max(min(iDetLevel3D,vardim1(stDetLevel3D)),1) parameters detLevel3D = stDetLevel3D[iDetLevel3D] endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! UI ! -------------------------------------------------------------------------
if need_ui_page_1 then put 1 if need_ui_page_2 then put 2 put 3 values "gs_ui_current_page" get(nsp)
if not(need_ui_page_1) and gs_ui_current_page = 1 then parameters gs_ui_current_page = 2 endif
if not(need_ui_page_2) and gs_ui_current_page = 2 then parameters gs_ui_current_page = 3 endif
if GLOB_UI_BUTTON_ID = 1 then parameters gs_ui_current_page = 1 if GLOB_UI_BUTTON_ID = 2 then parameters gs_ui_current_page = 2 if GLOB_UI_BUTTON_ID = 3 then parameters gs_ui_current_page = 3
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! 2D, 3D Representation ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ if GLOB_CONTEXT = 1 | GLOB_CONTEXT = 5 then for i = 1 to 255 put i next i
